<Base title="Attribution" description="Attribution and IP notices for Primo Guides.">
  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <h1>Attribution &amp; IP Notice</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2>Box art and game imagery</h2>
    <p>Box art and game imagery are the property of their respective publishers, shown for identification and editorial purposes under fair-dealing principles, sourced via IGDB (the Internet Game Database, owned by Twitch/Amazon). If any attribution is missing or wrong, please <a href="mailto:eevee.bork@icloud.com">tell us</a>.</p>

    <h2>Gameplay videos</h2>
    <p>Videos are embedded from their original creators on YouTube and remain their property. We link back to the source. We do not host video ourselves. Pressing play loads the YouTube player, which is subject to YouTube's own terms.</p>

    <h2>Written walkthroughs</h2>
    <p>Our written walkthroughs are original work, researched from multiple public sources and written from scratch. We do not reproduce text from other guides.</p>

    <h2>Missing or incorrect attribution</h2>
    <p>Email <a href="mailto:eevee.bork@icloud.com">eevee.bork@icloud.com</a> and we'll correct it promptly.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
